### Creating new Ingredient
POST http://localhost:8080/ingredients
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

name=Tomato1&spicy=true&veggie=false&amount=2

### Editing existing Ingredient
PATCH http://localhost:8080/ingredients/Pickles
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

amount=3

### Editing existing Ingredient
PATCH http://localhost:8080/ingredients/Test
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

spicy=true

### Deleting Ingredient
DELETE http://localhost:8080/ingredients/Pickles

### Getting Ingredients Pagination
GET http://localhost:8080/ingredients
page: 0
page-size: 12

### Get Ingredient by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/ingredients/Pickles

### Get Ingredients by Spicy
GET http://localhost:8080/ingredients?spicy=true

### Get all Pizzas that contain Ingredient
GET http://localhost:8080/ingredients/Pickles/pizzas

